  "body": "When using hardhat with TS regular error stack traces (coming from js not sol) are off. \r\n\r\nRepro: https://github.com/krzkaczor/typescript-solidity-dev-starter-kit/tree/kk/repro-stack-traces\r\n\r\nBasically error is:\r\n`      at ...typescript-solidity-dev-starter-kit/test/counter.ts:54:31`\r\nbut it should be line 14.\r\n\r\nI tried playing with tsconfig (enabling inline sourcemaps etc, bumping target). Stack traces seems to be fine in `hardhatconfig.ts` - they are only wrong in tests.\r\n\r\nAny ideas? I can work on this but I am not that familiar with codebase so any pointers would be great.",
