    "body": "I figured it out. This bug is triggered if you import anything from waffle directly in your tests. \r\n\r\nI used `rhlsthrm/typescript-solidity-dev-starter-kit` boilerplate which had this bug. \r\n\r\nHere's a PR to fix this in dev-starter-kit: https://github.com/rhlsthrm/typescript-solidity-dev-starter-kit/pull/19\r\n\r\nand here's a PR to lazy load ganache in waffle to avoid triggering this bug: https://github.com/EthWorks/Waffle/pull/471\r\n\r\n",
